transition is used to make a change from one state to another state (effect)
transition-property is used for the transition what we want (transition(change)in font-size,width..etc..)
transition-duration :2s etc(how long)
transition-timing-function:ease-in/ease-out/linear/steps..
transition-delay:2s..
Transition Shorthand
property name|duration|timing function|delay
